'''Aitro Koornacht''' was a member of the palace guard in the Court of [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Preedu III]] on [[Tamban]]<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>. He observed the astronomer known as the [[First Observer]] intimately involved with a woman in a [[groundcoach]]. The First Observer named the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]] after Koornacht in return for keeping his encounter a secret.<ref name="TCSWE" />

